<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Sixth Month • MommyGlow</title>

  <!-- Fonts & Icons -->
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&family=Dancing+Script:wght@700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.6.0/css/all.min.css">

  <style>
    :root {
      --pink: #e91e63;
      --pink-dark: #c2185b;
      --pink-glow: #ff4081;
      --light-pink: #fce4ec;
      --gold: #ffd700;
      --success: #4caf50;
      --danger: #f44336;
      --warning: #ff9800;
      --info: #2196f3;
      --purple: #9c27b0;
      --teal: #00bcd4;
      --green: #8bc34a;
    }

    * { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff0f5 0%, #fce4ec 40%, #f8bbd0 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      color: #444;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* Dreamy Wave Background */
    .wave-bg {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: -1;
    }
    .wave {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 0;
      width: 200%;
      height: 55vh;
      background: linear-gradient(transparent, rgba(233,30,99,0.12));
      animation: wave 24s linear infinite;
      opacity: 0.7;
    }
    .wave:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: -12s; opacity: 0.4; }
    @keyframes wave { 0% { transform: translateX(0); } 100% { transform: translateX(-50%); } }

    /* Glass Header */
    header {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
      backdrop-filter: blur(25px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(233,30,99,0.2);
      padding: 20px 60px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      z-index: 9999;
      box-shadow: 0 15px 50px rgba(233,30,99,0.3);
    }
    .logo {
      font-family: 'Dancing Script', cursive;
      font-size: 48px;
      font-weight: 800;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--pink), #ff6baf);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }
    .back-btn {
      padding: 14px 36px;
      background: var(--pink);
      color: white;
      border-radius: 50px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 35px rgba(233,30,99,0.4);
      transition: all 0.4s ease;
    }
    .back-btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-6px) scale(1.08);
      box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(233,30,99,0.55);
    }

    main {
      max-width: 1150px;
      margin: 150px auto 100px;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    /* Heartbeat + Glowing Title */
    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 3.8rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #c2185b, #e91e63, #ff4081, #ff6baf);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      animation: heartbeat 2.8s ease-in-out infinite, glow 4s ease-in-out infinite;
      text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255,64,129,0.4);
    }
    @keyframes heartbeat { 0%,100% { transform: scale(1); } 50% { transform: scale(1.05); } }
    @keyframes glow { 0%,100% { text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255,64,129,0.4); } 50% { text-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(255,64,129,0.7); } }

    .subtitle {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      color: #775555;
      max-width: 960px;
      margin: 0 auto 70px;
      font-weight: 500;
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-style: italic;
    }

    /* Floating Glass Cards */
    .section, .emergency-box, .family-box {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.97);
      backdrop-filter: blur(22px);
      border-radius: 32px;
      padding: 42px 38px;
      margin: 50px 0;
      box-shadow: 0 25px 70px rgba(233,30,99,0.25);
      border: 1px solid rgba(233,30,99,0.18);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: all 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
    }
    .section:hover, .emergency-box:hover, .family-box:hover {
      transform: translateY(-22px) scale(1.03);
      box-shadow: 0 60px 120px rgba(233,30,99,0.42);
    }
    .section::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -70%; left: -70%;
      width: 240%; height: 240%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,105,180,0.18) 0%, transparent 70%);
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 1s;
    }
    .section:hover::before { opacity: 1; }

    h2.section-title {
      font-size: 2.4rem;
      color: var(--pink-dark);
      margin-bottom: 32px;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
    }
    h2.section-title::after {
      content: '';
      width: 140px;
      height: 7px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--pink-glow), transparent);
      display: block;
      margin: 18px auto 0;
      border-radius: 50px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(255,64,129,0.6);
    }

    /* Do / Don't Grid */
    .flex-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 38px;
      margin-top: 24px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .flex-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap:24px; }
      h1 { font-size: 2.8rem; }
      main { margin: 130px auto 70px; padding: 0 15px; }
      .section, .emergency-box, .family-box { padding: 32px 26px; }
    }

    .do-box, .avoid-box {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
      padding: 32px;
      border-radius: 26px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      transition: all 0.5s ease;
    }
    .do-box { border-left: 8px solid var(--success); background: #f8fff8; }
    .avoid-box { border-left: 8px solid var(--danger); background: #fff8f8; }
    .do-box:hover, .avoid-box:hover { transform: translateY(-10px); }

    .do-box h4, .avoid-box h4 {
      font-size: 1.7rem;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
      text-align: center;
      padding-bottom: 12px;
      border-bottom: 4px solid;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .do-box h4 { color: var(--success); border-color: var(--success); }
    .avoid-box h4 { color: var(--danger); border-color: var(--danger); }

    li {
      padding: 16px 0;
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      position: relative;
      padding-left: 56px;
      transition: all 0.4s ease;
    }
    li:hover { transform: translateX(12px); }

    /* Sparkling Checkmarks */
    .do-item::before {
      content: "✓";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      top: 12px;
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      color: var(--success);
      animation: sparkle 2s infinite;
    }
    .avoid-item::before {
      content: "✕";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      top: 12px;
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      color: var(--danger);
    }
    @keyframes sparkle {
      0%,100% { transform: scale(1) rotate(0); text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(76,175,80,0.6); }
      50% { transform: scale(1.3) rotate(10deg); text-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(76,175,80,0.9); }
    }

    /* Golden Shimmer Tip Box */
    .tip-box {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff8e1 0%, #ffecb3 50%, #ffe082 100%);
      border: 2px solid var(--gold);
      padding: 24px 32px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      margin: 32px 0;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #e65100;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(255,215,0,0.3);
      animation: shimmer 6s infinite;
    }
    .tip-box::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -50%; left: -50%;
      width: 200%; height: 200%;
      background: linear-gradient(45deg, transparent 30%, rgba(255,255,255,0.4) 50%, transparent 70%);
      transform: rotate(30deg);
      animation: shine 8s infinite;
    }
    @keyframes shimmer { 0%,100% { transform: translateY(0); } 50% { transform: translateY(-10px); } }
    @keyframes shine { 0% { transform: translateX(-100%) rotate(30deg); } 100% { transform: translateX(100%) rotate(30deg); } }

    /* Emergency & Family */
    .emergency-box {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffebee 0%, #ffcdd2 100%);
      border: 3px solid #ff5252;
      box-shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(244,67,54,0.3);
    }
    .family-box {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e3f2fd 0%, #bbdefb 100%);
      border: 3px solid #42a5f5;
      box-shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(33,150,243,0.3);
    }

    /* Pastel Section Colors */
    .diet     { border-left: 8px solid var(--warning); }
    .activity { border-left: 8px solid var(--info); }
    .mental   { border-left: 8px solid var(--pink); }
    .lifestyle{ border-left: 8px solid var(--purple); }
    .medical  { border-left: 8px solid var(--teal); }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="wave-bg">
    <div class="wave"></div>
    <div class="wave"></div>
  </div>

  <header>
    <div class="logo">MommyGlow</div>
    <div>
      <% if(name){ %>
        <a href="/precautions" class="back-btn">Back to Journey</a>
      <% } else { %>
        <a href="/" class="back-btn">Back to Home</a>
      <% } %>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <h1>Sixth Month of Pregnancy</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Your baby is practicing breathing, growing eyebrows & eyelashes, and dancing to your voice — those strong kicks are pure love letters from within</p>

    <!-- Diet -->
    <div class="section diet">
      <h2 class="section-title">Diet Precautions</h2>
      <div class="flex-grid">
        <div class="do-box">
          <h4>Include</h4>
          <ul>
            <li class="do-item">Iron-rich foods: spinach, beetroot, raisins, jaggery</li>
            <li class="do-item">Protein: milk, paneer, eggs, fish (well cooked)</li>
            <li class="do-item">Calcium: curd, ragi, almonds, sesame</li>
            <li class="do-item">Omega-3: walnuts, flax seeds for brain development</li>
            <li class="do-item">Fiber foods for constipation: fruits + vegetables</li>
            <li class="do-item">Drink 3–3.5 liters water</li>
            <li class="do-item">Include buttermilk, coconut water for hydration</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="avoid-box">
          <h4>Avoid</h4>
          <ul>
            <li class="avoid-item">Excess sugary foods (risk of gestational diabetes)</li>
            <li class="avoid-item">Bakery/snacks/oily foods</li>
            <li class="avoid-item">Too much salt → swelling increases</li>
            <li class="avoid-item">Aerated drinks and caffeine (>1 cup/day)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="tip-box">Important: Continue Iron & Calcium supplements regularly</div>
    </div>

    <!-- Activity -->
    <div class="section activity">
      <h2 class="section-title">Physical Activity & Exercise</h2>
      <div class="flex-grid">
        <div class="do-box"><h4>Do</h4><ul>
          <li class="do-item">Brisk walking 30–45 mins daily</li>
          <li class="do-item">Prenatal yoga with certified trainer</li>
          <li class="do-item">Kegel exercises for pelvic support</li>
          <li class="do-item">Stretch legs before sleep (prevents cramps)</li>
        </ul></div>
        <div class="avoid-box"><h4>Avoid</h4><ul>
          <li class="avoid-item">Lifting heavy objects</li>
          <li class="avoid-item">High-speed movement or jerks</li>
          <li class="avoid-item">Sleeping straight on back</li>
          <li class="avoid-item">Long bike or bumpy road travel</li>
        </ul></div>
      </div>
      <div class="tip-box">Use pillow support under legs for better blood flow</div>
    </div>

    <!-- Body & Lifestyle + Normal Symptoms -->
    <div class="section lifestyle">
      <h2 class="section-title">Body & Lifestyle Care</h2>
      <ul>
        <li class="do-item">Left-side sleeping (best for baby oxygen supply)</li>
        <li class="do-item">Wear loose cotton clothes</li>
        <li class="do-item">Use stretch-mark oil or coconut oil regularly</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="tip-box" style="border-left-color:#8bc34a; background:#f1f8e9; color:#33691e;">
        Possible Symptoms This Month (All Normal):
        <ul style="margin:12px 0 0 20px; text-align:left;">
          <li>Heartburn • Back pain • Leg cramps</li>
          <li>Swelling in feet • Increased appetite</li>
        </ul>
        <strong>Manage with good posture & frequent rest</strong>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Medical -->
    <div class="section medical">
      <h2 class="section-title">Medical Checkups in Month-6</h2>
      <ul>
        <li class="do-item">Gestational Diabetes Screening (GTT Test)</li>
        <li class="do-item">Hb (Hemoglobin) test</li>
        <li class="do-item">BP monitoring every visit</li>
        <li class="do-item">Fetal Movement observation</li>
        <li class="do-item">Ultrasound if doctor advises</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="tip-box">Track baby kicks daily → Strong sign of baby health</div>
    </div>

    <!-- Emergency -->
    <div class="emergency-box">
      <h2 class="section-title">Emergency Symptoms - Contact Doctor Immediately</h2>
      <ul>
        <li class="avoid-item">Sudden gush of fluid / water breaking</li>
        <li class="avoid-item">Severe abdominal pain or bleeding</li>
        <li class="avoid-item">Persistent dizziness / fainting</li>
        <li class="avoid-item">Severe swelling or sudden weight gain</li>
        <li class="avoid-item">Fever >38°C or difficulty breathing</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Family Support -->
    <div class="family-box">
      <h2 class="section-title">Family Support & Tips</h2>
      <ul>
        <li class="do-item">Encourage calm environment, reduce stress</li>
        <li class="do-item">Husband/family to help with chores</li>
        <li class="do-item">Discuss birthing plan and hospital visits</li>
        <li class="do-item">Maintain emotional wellbeing and bonding with baby</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

  </main>

</body>
</html>
